				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player and Minthara wake up in a private room at the Elfsong tavern, having spent the night together after saving the city and destroying the netherbrain. \r\n\r\nMinthara is a little bit upset that the player didn't seize control of the brain and become the new Absolute, but she's in love with them and forgives them. And then dreams about their next conquests."
				}
